headline: FactSet (FDS) Valuation Check After Mixed Quarterly Results and Analyst Price Target Cuts
summary: FactSet Research Systems (FDS) has been under pressure after quarterly results showed a revenue beat but an earnings miss, followed by a wave of analyst caution and lower expectations that sharpened focus on margins. See our latest analysis for FactSet Research Systems. Those mixed results and the recent Arcesium partnership come after a bruising stretch, with the share price down sharply on a year to date basis despite a 1 month share price return of 10.7 percent and a 5 year total...
